The Lagos State Police Commissioner, Edgar Imohimi, speaking to Channels on Monday, declared the controversial dancehall singer Burna boy, wanted, in connection with the robbery and assault case on singer, Mr. 2Kay, which occurred on October 22, 2017, in his room at Eko Hotel and Suites after performing at 2Face's Buckwyld and Breathless Concert. He said, "At about 2am, someone knocked on the door of Mr 2Kay's room and introduced himself as a room service official from the reception. Mr 2Kay opened the door and four men entered with a gun.